{
  "stem": "7600.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And she did a lot of the cooking because my mother went to the store with my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She worked in the store.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So she did a lot of the cooking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She was a wonderful cook.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I wish I would have her danishes that she made and her strudels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She was a wonderful baker and cooker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she learned to cook without being kosher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I mean, she grumbled, and she was an unhappy woman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she and my father always had words.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But it wasn't very serious because she knew there was nothing she could do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She had no place to go, because her sisters and her brothers wouldn't have taken her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They could have probably taken her in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She would have been more happy there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But, in those days, widows lived with their daughters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "That was the rule.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And the rule-- that kind of a rule was hard to break, I guess.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because I couldn't understand, when we went to Vienna she had all those relatives, and not one of them ever said, you can come and live with us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They had room.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But-- especially she had a brother who never married who was also a dentist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he lived alone with-- with the housekeeper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "She certainly could have lived with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But he never said so, and she never said so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She always lived with us until she died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "This was the-- I guess this was the norm in those days, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Because I don't know any-- all the other widows I knew, they always lived with their daughters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I don't know what they did if they didn't have daughters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I guess they had to live with their daughter-in-laws, which wasn't too happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
